{"tid":1984891,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"女性乳房圖竟嚇倒無數網民","createTime":"2020-04-22T18:29:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-22T18:53:58.000Z","uid":231337,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b29b211c3006220e53ff2faebff0692590396e18","tid":1984891,"uid":231337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T18:29:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iSTLa5w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiSTLa5w.png&h=a1d10f11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n乳腺管？這是什麼？為什麼是這個樣子？這東西真的在我體內嗎？我再不想要乳房了。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以上都是人類乳腺管照片在網上瘋傳後，用戶在社交媒體上的反應。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在女性的乳房中，有製造人奶的乳腺組織被分割成15-20片葉。而圖中的小導管，負責將人奶從乳腺組織送往乳頭。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n也許這個事實並不廣為人知，令許多網民看到女性肌肉圖後覺得難以接受。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/science-48062111?at_custom4=34960048-84A4-11EA-915F-BD0E933C408C&amp;at_custom3=BBC+Chinese+(Traditional\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fscience-48062111%3Fat_custom4%3D34960048-84A4-11EA-915F-BD0E933C408C%26at_custom3%3DBBC%2BChinese%2B%28Traditional&d=uNNx3RetO4MSseDCYlD6CiNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=244daa9a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fscience-48062111%3Fat_custom4%3D34960048-84A4-11EA-915F-BD0E933C408C%26at_custom3%3DBBC%2BChinese%2B%28Traditional&h=09b895d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/science-48062111?at_custom4=34960048-84A4-11EA-915F-BD0E933C408C&amp;at_custom3=BBC+Chinese+(Traditional</a>)&amp;at_campaign=64&amp;at_medium=custom7&amp;at_custom2=facebook_page&amp;at_custom1=%5Bpost+type%5D"},{"pid":"5d7f36cb73487c5de73e1051cc0e8e942e8782a7","tid":1984891,"uid":129531,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T18:32:50.000Z","msg":"bam<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de4849857e2f281b80b04eb58594eed7d5963e8a","tid":1984